title: Did Republican Dean Browning tweet "I'm a black gay man"?
subtitle: Twitter users believe that the tweet was intended to come out through an alternative, phantom account to enhance support for republican issues.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: Dean Browning, a white man who ran and lost in 2020 the Republican elections to the United States House of Pennsylvania 7, tweeted, "I'm a gay black man" from his Twitter check account.
